m_q.target_metric: Nations that won at least one gold medal but won zero silver medals
sub_questions: Which nations have Gold medal count greater than 0?
Which nations have Silver medal count equal to 0?
What is the intersection of nations with gold medals and no silver medals?

format_notes: Data contains multiple ranking systems (appears to have separate rankings for different regions or competitions)
Rank values repeat (e.g., multiple rank 1, 2, etc.), suggesting different medal tables
All numeric columns use Int64 dtype

output_format_requirements: Only include nations meeting both criteria: Gold > 0 AND Silver = 0
